    "body": "Yes, this has never had anything to do with IPython, it's always affected _all_ distutils-installed scripts, but IPython is often the only such script inherited into a virtualenv.\n\nIt should be considered a virtualenv bug that they don't patch the #! line of python scripts.\n"
